videos.headline: Iowa takes INT return 88 yards for TD
videos.description: Maryland QB Perry Hills throws the ball right to Iowa's Desmond King and then watches the Hawkeye go 88 yards the other way to the house. Iowa goes up 31-7 in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Maryland answers back in a flash
videos.description: Maryland's Marshall Koehn shows off his blazing speed, going the full 100 yards untouched on a kickoff return for a touchdown.
